sequenceDiagram
    participant Local as Local launcher
    participant Colab as Colab L4
    participant HF as Hugging Face
    participant GPU as Model process

    Local->>Local: Build checksummed code/data bundle
    Local->>Colab: Create L4 session and upload bundle
    Colab->>HF: Fetch exact pinned base revision
    Colab->>GPU: Run smoke/evaluation/training
    loop At every complete checkpoint
        GPU->>Colab: Atomically archive checkpoint
        Colab->>Local: Download and verify checkpoint
    end
    GPU->>Colab: Write metrics, logs, and final adapter
    Colab->>Local: Download result archive
    Local->>Local: Validate hashes and required files
    Local->>Colab: Stop session in cleanup trap

